All Implemented Interfaces:
NodeVisitor<ExprNode,Void>
public class SubstituteGlobalsVisitor
extends AbstractExprNodeVisitor<Void>

Visitor for substituting values of compile-time globals and/or for checking that all globals are defined by the compile-time globals map.

Important: Do not use outside of Soy code (treat as superpackage-private).

Use with SoytreeUtils.visitAllExprs(com.google.template.soy.soytree.SoyFileSetNode, com.google.template.soy.exprtree.AbstractExprNodeVisitor).

To do substitution only, set shouldAssertNoUnboundGlobals to false in the constructor. To do substitution and checking, set shouldAssertNoUnboundGlobals to true.
